{"tid":490321,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(平成拉打限定)入黎分享下你心目中嘅TOP3","createTime":"2017-12-05T13:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T11:18:31.000Z","uid":84544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1c009c9acbff2bf2cadab6e5ff41e5b4c20968","tid":490321,"uid":84544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"眼見平成就黎完結 <br />\n諗番起原來平成拉打其實已經做咗有成十七年了 <br />\n真喺不得不認老 <br />\n各位巴絲不如分享下自己心目中嘅各種TOP3當喺對自己回憶嘅一種重溫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7754776c11c9ade729094bd6d95b8589ad49fb89","tid":490321,"uid":84544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"等我分享下我心目中嘅TOP3先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>劇集TOP3</ins><br />\n<br />\n第一名我會簡佢  - Kuuga<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/8/7070/26613246443_08abab5d38_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F8%2F7070%2F26613246443_08abab5d38_b.jpg&h=d12c9197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為第一個平成嘅拉打,我覺得KUUGA呢套劇喺各方面真喺做得好好<br />\n未知生命體用嘅語言設定,拉打嘅車技,超高成本和高危嘅動作戲(有冇人仲記得喺架飛機上面拍打戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ),眾人嘅演技,劇情方面一條同女王果條線又喺好正  好可惜冇劇場版寫埋落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主角五代雄介由討厭戰鬥去到最後為左守護大家而戰鬥呢個轉變真喺好感動 <br />\n最後之戰同一條告別果Part <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同零號打果陣一個一路打一路笑 而雄介一路打一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最後雙雙倒地果下真喺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽聞因為佢喺第一代平成拉打劇所以最後果集話佢去左唔知邊度旅行而唔喺同0號一齊死<br />\n最可惜喺冇劇場版同埋後期為左趕進度而跳過左好多劇情 不過呢套係我心目依然喺NO.1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &amp;lt;----呢個手勢每次一用就諗起雄介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然一個好嘅OP都唔少得(中,日版OP都好正,日版果首ED歌詞大意都好有意思)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二名我會簡佢-龍騎<br />\n<img src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3784/9591603621_a24a872f22_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm4.staticflickr.com%2F3784%2F9591603621_a24a872f22_o.jpg&h=675f0553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當經歷完兩套相似嘅拉打劇集 馬上搞搞新意思:鏡世界,拉打VS拉打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,怪物嘅來源,蓮同真司由敵變友嘅互動,吾郎嘅搞笑場面 我果陣睇真心覺得好睇好有創意 <br />\n<br />\n而且反派我相信大家都唔會忘記佢 契約王-王蛇 <br />\n<img src=\"http://farm6.staticflickr.com/5321/9591604451_9e4901a203_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm6.staticflickr.com%2F5321%2F9591604451_9e4901a203_o.jpg&h=90b4d967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三隻契約獸,利用鏡能力走佬 連最後死果下都夠哂型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第三名我反而會簡呢個-Decade<br />\n<img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4019/4649872654_88b27182bc_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.static.flickr.com%2F4019%2F4649872654_88b27182bc_b.jpg&h=3c861b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可能好多人都唔鐘意呢套 又覺得個外型好柒,又搵唔番當年果D演員黎做,醜化KUUGA之類,屈機,<br />\n 不過我鐘意佢嘅變身能力夠屈機(結果戰隊果邊馬上整套海賊戰隊豪快者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n雖然後期劇情接唔上(寫劇本果個走左 )真。劇情版,結局又唔見埋  但睇佢一兩集喺一個系列咁回顧番之前咁多期既平成拉打都有一種感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先打住咁多先 遲D再打埋我心目中嘅TOP3反派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140504a06daab93abef2f1b3069d2d12ccded447","tid":490321,"uid":31816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"個人認為decade前期平成拉打平行世界寫得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係後期昭和拉打果陣出事，但decade真係印像好深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4412876cd219ac0efc6c90b160814e7a62abda76","tid":490321,"uid":21460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"舊平成劇情:<br />\n1. 龍騎<br />\n2. 電王<br />\n3. 古迦<br />\n<br />\n新平成劇情:<br />\n1. W<b